<L>__{interior henry's house moments later}
<A>__{henry enters. hangs up his down jacket on a row of hooks. it's clean and ordinary in here. his wife, debbie, is in the kitchen. she's wearing a nurses uniform. henry notices the dining room table set for one for breakfast. eggs, bacon, sausage. he's a little surprised. debbie appears. lays down the toast.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{smells good.}
<C>__{debbie}
<D>__{sit down.}
